description: The 77 Shiki Senjutsu Hokou Sentouki Gekishin is a Japanese variant of the F-4 Phantom, the first TSF produced. It has been since mostly replaced by the Type-82 Zuikaku and Type-97 Fubuki and many Type-97 were designated as training machines for new cadets.
name: 77 Shiki Senjutsu Hokou Sentouki Gekishin
